      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>couscous</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> to a heatproof bowl with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover with a tea towel and set aside until serving</p>",
